VATION/Prospect Activation Intent AND Product Type = ISP AND Orders exists.\nBYOD SIM: confirmation page with Orders AND Product Name = BYOS SIM or eSIM, SIM Card, Tarjeta SIM, Mobile Internet SIM Card, or Tarjeta SIM para Internet movil AND Flow = activation intent.\nRemoves HITS where OS = Google Android AND Order ID (v14) does not exist AND Page Layout State (v86) = Native App.\nOrders Postpaid Flow / UVNB Postpaid Flow.' AS apx_build_details,'HSI AND BYOD ORDERS\nIN-STORE/SCREEN-SHARE\nPROSPECT FILTERS\nANDROID GHOST HITS' AS apx_excl_labels,'Excludes HSI and BYOD orders from Postpaid count.\nIn-store and screen-share sessions excluded via Unassisted Proxy.\nAll prospect filters applied.\nAndroid native app ghost hits (missing Order ID) excluded.' AS apx_excl_details,CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS apx_glossary_category
UNION ALL SELECT 17 AS apx_sort_order,'orders_hsi_flow' AS apx_id,'Orders - HSI Flow' AS apx_label,'Metric' AS apx_record_type,'Bottom Funnel' AS apx_funnel_stage,3 AS apx_funnel_sort,'Orders Unassisted' AS apx_category,17 AS apx_category_sort,'Home Internet (HSI)' AS apx_scope,'HSI' AS apx_lob,TRUE AS apx_is_subflow,'orders_unassisted_overall' AS apx_parent_id,TRUE AS apx_subflows_summable,'Adobe Analytics -> BigQuery (via Improvado)' AS apx_source_system,'BigQuery' AS apx_source_platform,'prj-dbi-prd-1.ds_dbi_improvado_master.sdi_raw_adobe_pp_pulse_pro_orders_unassisted_daily_tmo' AS apx_source_table,'Improvado' AS apx_data_owner,'Daily at 9 AM PT' AS apx_refresh_cadence,'Home Internet orders completed fully online by a prospect - confirming a new HSI subscriber acquired through the digital channel.' AS apx_definition,'Part of Orders (Unassisted) total.' AS apx_sum_warning,'orders_hsi_flow' AS apx_cvr_numerator_id,'uvnb_hsi_flow' AS apx_cvr_denominator_id,'LAYER 1\nLAYER 2\nLAYER 3\nLAYER 4 - HSI ORDERS\nCONDITION - SITE NAME\nCONDITION - FLOW NAME\nCONDITION - PRODUCT TYPE\nCONDITION - ORDERS\nCVR %' AS apx_build_labels,'Universal filters.\nProspect qualifiers.\n[DA] Unassisted Proxy - removes in-store and screen-share sessions.\n[DA] HSI Prospect Orders - includes HITS where ALL four conditions are true simultaneously.\nSite Name (v18) = TLife App OR TMO.\nFlow Name (v154) = ACTIVATION Intent OR Prospect Activation Intent OR Intencion de activacion de prospecto Intent (via [sdi] Activation Intent).\nProduct Type (v100) = ISP.\nOrders exists.\nOrders HSI Flow / UVNB HSI Flow.' AS apx_build_details,'REQUIREMENT\nOTHER LOBS\nUNASSISTED PROXY' AS apx_excl_labels,'Requires ISP product type AND HSI activation flow.\nWill not count Postpaid or BYOD orders.\nUnassisted proxy also applied.' AS apx_excl_details,CAST(NULL AS STRING) AS apx_glossary_category
